metadata.dc:description: Contribution of 2 cases of post-ESWL subcapsular haematoma in patients with HBP. One of them underwent surgical drainage. In the second case a more conservative attitude was followed. Review of related literature.
metadata.dc:title: Hematoma subcapsular tras ESWL.
[Subcapsular hematoma after ESWL].
